data.description: RARE OPPORTUNITY TO OWN THE BEST LOCATION IN TOWN! Iconic Sanders Beach property just steps from Lake Coeur d'Alene. Here's your chance to live the North Idaho dream in Coeur d'Alene's most prestigious neighborhood on one of the best streets in town - the much sought-after Lakeshore Drive in the charming enclave of Sanders Beach. What a fabulous place to live a fabulous life. This Art Deco inspired home built in the 1930s is ready for a major renovation offering the lucky new owners major upside potential. Redesign, reimagine and rebuild to your personal specifications and, once complete, you will have an absolute gem, one-of-a-kind home with spectacular views in an extraordinary location. The home sits on a private, generously sized .18-acre lot and is one of the few homes on Lakeshore Drive to enjoy the picturesque views and amazing location without the heavy burden of waterfront taxes. Across the street is one of two public Sanders Beach City beaches (public parking is not allowed on either side of the street in this section.)  Put your boat in the water down the street at the 11th Street Marina, which has deeded boat slips available for purchase. This prime location is also walking distance to Tubb's Hill, McEuen Park, the award-winning Coeur d'Alene Library, the CdA Resort, City Beach, and Sherman Avenue where you and your loved ones can enjoy all the shops, bars, restaurants and activities downtown Coeur d'Alene has to offer. The possibilities are endless. Agents: see private notes for showing restrictions.
